&= \frac{1}{2} M_1 \sqrt{GM_{\rm p}a_1} \frac{\dot{a}_1}{a_1} + \frac{1}{2} M_2 \sqrt{GM_{\rm p} a_2} \frac{\dot{a}_2}{a_2} \nonumber \\
&= \frac{1}{2} \frac{\dot{a}_1}{a_1} \big( J_1 + J_2 \big) \, .
